nodes.text: Neb Neb Goodrow was a bongo racer who along with fellow racer Spleed Nukkels was accused of collision, endangering the lives of others, and giving the sport a bad name. Racers Zak Quiglee and Friggy Squig tried to get them banned, but their charges were rejected by the Gungan race commissioner.
Goodrow later participated in the Otoh Gunga Challenge. Neb Neb wasn't in the lead at the beginning but quickly caught up. However, later in the race Goodrow collided with Spleed, and lost the race.
